  "text": "In Natural Language Processing, the term \"Named Entity\" refers to special information units such as people, organizations, location names, numerical expression [CITATION_1] . Identifying the references to these special entities in text is a crucial step toward Language Understanding. Thus, there have been many works on these areas.",
